## EXAMPLE FINDING

```yaml
finding:
  id: QA-001
  category: QA
  subcategory: Error Handling
  severity: HIGH
  file: src/pages/forms/DailyEquipmentInspectionForm.tsx
  line: 280-290
  observed_condition: |
    Form submission does not handle network failure. If API 
    returns error, user sees no feedback and form state is lost.
  evidence: |
    const handleSubmit = async (data) => {
      await submitInspection(data); // No try-catch
      navigate('/dashboard'); // Assumes success
    };
  impact: |
    On network error, user loses all form data with no indication
    of failure. Must re-enter entire form.
  recommendation: |
    1. Wrap in try-catch
    2. Show error toast on failure
    3. Keep form data on error
    4. Add retry mechanism
  dod: |
    1. Simulate network error (Network tab)
    2. Error message displayed to user
    3. Form data preserved
    4. User can retry submission
  effort: S
  dependencies: none
```

